name: Cybersquash Switchbrain (UNLOCKABLE 3D Model)
description:
If you purchase this NFT, you can also request and receive the static 3D model obj files that I can share/send to you. Fully outfitted/armored character, with full modeled underlying separate nude figure body. Unlockable 3D package will include a basic set of maps too (Full 4k texture sets will not be included).

3D character asset designed originally as part of a project for a mobile game developer. The character ended up not being used, as the project was shelved, backlogged indefinitely in 2019. It's a fully completed character, modeled and textured, retopologized, and optimized in low poly version for video game use. Zbrush, Cinema4D, Octane, Substance Painter were used in creation.
